---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="House Painters Greater Hobart | Full Region Coverage"
  description="House painters across Greater Hobart — inner suburbs, northern suburbs, Kingborough and the eastern shore. Interior, exterior, roof, heritage and commercial painting. Free quote."
  canonical="https://hobarthousepainters.com.au/hobart-region/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Greater Hobart &middot; full coverage</span>
      <h1>House painters across <span class="accent">Greater Hobart</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From the heritage inner suburbs to the northern suburbs, Kingborough to
        the south and the eastern shore, we paint right across Greater Hobart.
        Interior, exterior, roof, heritage and commercial &mdash; one local team,
        proper cold-climate preparation, low-VOC paints, and a fixed price.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>Each with local detail &mdash; housing stock, heritage and lead-paint notes, the weather and salt exposure that shape the work.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/sandy-bay/">Sandy Bay</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/glenorchy/">Glenorchy</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/kingston/">Kingston</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/moonah/">Moonah</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/new-town/">New Town</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Other Hobart suburbs we cover.</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Bellerive</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Battery Point</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lindisfarne</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Lenah Valley</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">North Hobart</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">South Hobart</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">West Hobart</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Mount Stuart</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Howrah</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Claremont</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Rosny</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Blackmans Bay</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Taroona</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Derwent Park</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Montrose</span>
          <span class="area-pill area-pill-static">Rosetta</span>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Different parts of Hobart, different painting needs.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Heritage inner suburbs</strong> (Sandy Bay, Battery Point, New
          Town, Mount Stuart): Federation, Georgian and weatherboard homes, much
          of it pre-1970 and carrying lead paint &mdash; conservation-sensitive,
          lead-safe work to AS 4361.2 and period-correct colour.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Northern suburbs</strong> (Glenorchy, Moonah, Claremont,
          Montrose): post-war and brick-veneer family homes, rentals, unit blocks
          and a busy commercial strip &mdash; durable exterior recoats, fast rental
          turnarounds and strata work.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Kingborough and the south</strong> (Kingston, Blackmans Bay,
          Margate): newer estates, 1980s&ndash;90s homes, renovations and new
          builds, plus coastal exposure closer to the water.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>The eastern shore</strong> (Bellerive, Howrah, Lindisfarne,
          Rosny): a mix of established and newer homes across the Derwent, with
          salt-air exposure on river-facing exteriors.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">What every Hobart paint job has in common.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Proper preparation</strong> &mdash; wash, mould treatment, sand, fill and prime before any topcoat. The part that makes it last in this climate.</li>
          <li><strong>Paints rated for cool, damp maritime conditions</strong>, and low-VOC interior paints as standard.</li>
          <li><strong>Lead-safe practice (AS 4361.2)</strong> on pre-1970 homes &mdash; no exceptions.</li>
          <li><strong>AS/NZS 2311 workmanship</strong> and WorkSafe Tasmania height safety on every job.</li>
          <li><strong>A fixed, itemised quote</strong> &mdash; not a vague hourly guess.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five services</span>
      <h2>What we do.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/interior-painting/"><h3>Interior house painting</h3><p>Walls, ceilings, trim and doors. Low-VOC paints, neat finish, floors protected.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/exterior-painting/"><h3>Exterior house painting</h3><p>Weatherboard, render and brick. Cold-climate prep built to last 7&ndash;10 years.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/roof-painting/"><h3>Roof painting &amp; coating</h3><p>Metal and tile cleaned, repaired, primed and coated. Rust treated.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/heritage-painting/"><h3>Heritage &amp; weatherboard</h3><p>Federation and Georgian homes, lead-safe to AS 4361.2, period-correct colour.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/commercial-painting/"><h3>Commercial &amp; strata</h3><p>Shopfronts, offices and body-corporate exteriors. Low-disruption scheduling.</p><span class="svc-link">See &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free painting quote anywhere in Greater Hobart.</h2>
        <p>Inner suburbs, northern suburbs, Kingborough or the eastern shore. Proper prep, fixed price.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
